description: A finite sequence associated with the Lie algebra E_8.
comments: The g.f. (5-6*z+2*z**2)/(z-1)**4 conjectured by _Simon Plouffe_ in his 1992 dissertation is wrong.
references: E. B. Dynkin, Semisimple subalgebras of semisimple Lie algebras, Am. Math. Soc. Translations, Series 2, Vol. 6, 1957, pp. 111-244, esp. p. 211.
links: Simon Plouffe, Approximations de séries génératrices et quelques conjectures, Dissertation, Université du Québec à Montréal, 1992.
Simon Plouffe, 1031 Generating Functions and Conjectures, Université du Québec à Montréal, 1992.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
